.entry-header
About
Established in 1995
Our local team provides on-site management and property maintenance.
We are a family-owned group of investors, with a portfolio of five properties located in Okeechobee, Florida. All properties are managed by one team.  Our team strives to provide clean, comfortable, and safe environments for all homeowners.  We provide long-term lot rental solutions for your mobile home, RV, or camper.
We look forward to your stay.
